<p>Both options work best for cases of mild to moderate crowding. SmileDirectClubâs aligners straighten teeth without buttons, attachments, or teeth filings. Unlike with metal braces, your teen will be able to eat their favorite foods and maintain good oral health habits like brushing and flossing without brackets in the way. <a href="http://smiledirectclub.com/parents/">Learn More &gt;</a></p>
      
